go install github.com/spf13/cobra-cli@latest
* Installing Cobra, you will get create commands like instructions of git-cli, nvm-cli and others

Initializing with cobra
* cobra-cli init

Adding new command
* cobra-cli add ping

To run a new command:
* go run main.go category

To add a new command "create" that belongs to category
* cobra-cli add create -p 'categoryCmd'

To add a new command "list" that belongs to category
* cobra-cli add list -p 'categoryCmd'

After add StringP using shorthand:
* go run main.go category -n=X

Joining 2 commands(flags):
* go run main.go category -n=categoria -e

Joining 3 commands(flags)
* go run main.go category -n=categoria -e --ID=10